data.description: This home completed in 2021 is still like new! Upgrades include a fully fenced backyard, reverse osmosis system, garbage disposal, blackout blinds upstairs, and closet storage racks. On the main level you have 1 full bath, living/dining room and a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops and easy close cabinets. Upstairs is an additional bonus area great for movie nights, another full bath and 3 bedrooms which includes the primary bedroom. This home is located on a cul-de-sac and close to parks, golf, trails, shopping, schools and more. Be sure to view the 3D virtual tour.
